message.content: cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.FL, cs.ET - This paper is about formal methods and their implementation, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper specifically focuses on the B method, which is a formal specification language and tool that falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and logic (cs.LO). The use of Coq, a proof assistant, also falls under logic (cs.LO) and formal languages (cs.FL). Finally, the paper discusses the implementation of a proved prover, which falls under the category of emerging technologies (cs.ET).
